The SAM (ARM) family needs a (slightly) different modifications in the USB core, so:
When using arduino-1.5.5, copy the files:
    From    To
    avr     $arduino_root/hardware/arduino/avr/cores/arduino/
    sam     $arduino_root/hardware/arduino/sam/cores/arduino/USB/

In older versions (1.0.x):
    From    To
    avr     $arduino_root/hardware/arduino/cores/arduino

